

game_information {
   game_name                    = The Undersea Game
   game_version                 = 0.5.0
   game_shortname               = undersea
   written_by                   = Tierney Cooper
   uuid                         = de65f167-af2b-428f-9c19-ce1c7da15c85
   year_of_release              = 2021
   copyright_message            = (C) Tierney Cooper
   short_synopsis               = Find your way to the temple under the sea.
}


start_at = under_the_sea

## Defines locations in the world

locations {
   under_the_sea      : location "You're outside a cave under the sea. This is your home. To the west lies a mangrove forest." ;
   trench  : location "You're outside a trench. Down below, you spy the temple. To the north, a pile of rocks." ;
   rocky_canyon : location "You're in a rocky canyon." ;
   temple : location "You're at the undersea temple.";
   mangrove : location "You're in a mangrove forest. Deep, deep down, you see something shiny." ;
   sunken_island : location "You're on a sunken island in the middle of the mangrove forest. There's a pile of diamonds here." graphic="mangrove";
}

# Defines things in the world (scenery cannot be carried)

objects {
   diamond : object "a diamond" msg="Shiny. Shiny and powerful." at="sunken_island";
   witch : scenery "a witch" at = "trench" msg="A witch named Rainbow.";
   golden_scale : object "a golden scale" msg="Beautiful.";
   fish : scenery "a fish" at = "rocky_canyon" msg="A fish named Ruby. She has shiny, golden scales.";
   diamond_holder : scenery "an empty diamond holder" at="temple" msg="Looks like it could hold a diamond.";
}
   
connections {

   ## Connects locations together (bidirectional)
   
   from, direction, to = [
      under_the_sea, north, trench,
      under_the_sea, west, mangrove,
      trench, north, rocky_canyon,
      trench, down_oneway, temple,
      mangrove, down, sunken_island,
   ]
}

barriers {

   block_trench : block {
      location = trench
      message = You can't go that way.
      block_when_not_carried = diamond
      show_blocked_exit = false
   }
   block_temple : block {
      location           = temple
      message            = The witch is blocking your way. Perhaps she'd like something shiny?
      block_when_exists  = witch
      show_blocked_exit  = true
   }
   
} 

## Print the objective when the game starts

on_startup {
   : print "Welcome to the Undersea Game !" ;
   : print "You're a mermaid named Jewel." ;
   : print "Find your way to the temple." ;
   : press_any_key ;
}

## Execute this every time a player moves or redescribes a location

on_describe {
   : if (is_at "under_the_sea" && is_carried "diamond") {
      : print "You feel the power of the diamond flowing through you." ;
      : print "To the north, you can see a trench that was previously invisible." ;
   }
}

## Test VERB NOUN that the player types and executes conditional actions

on_command {
   : match "give scale"  {
      : if (is_present "witch" && is_carried "golden_scale") {
         : print_graphic "trench_2" ;
         : set_graphic { target = "trench" ; graphic = "trench_2" } ;
         : print   "The witch runs off to hide the golden scale. You can probably enter the temple now!" ;
         : destroy "golden_scale" ;
         : destroy "witch" ;
      }
   }
   : match "take scale" {
      : if (is_present "fish") {
         : print "Ruby is happy to give you one of her golden scales." ;
         : create "golden_scale" target="inventory";
      }
   }
   : match "give diamond;put diamond;place diamond" {
      : if (is_carried "diamond" && is_present "witch") {
         : print "The witch cackles. Diamonds are shiny, but she wants something a little more aquatic." ;
      }
      : if (is_carried "diamond" && is_present "diamond_holder") {
         : print "You put the diamond into the diamond holder. YOU WIN!";
         : win_game;
      }
   }
}



assets {
   graphics {
      mangrove : base64_png "";
      rocky_canyon : base64_png "";
      temple : base64_png "";
      trench : base64_png "";
      trench_2 : base64_png "";
      under_the_sea : base64_png "";
   }
}
